      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Clean, honest car in fair condition and priced to sell. It runs and drives, and it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone looking for dependable basic transportation. Expect normal wear, cosmetic blemishes, and age-related imperfections, but overall it\u2019s a solid vehicle with plenty of life left for the right owner.",
