    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready to serve as a practical daily driver, this vehicle offers straightforward value for anyone seeking dependable basic transportation without a big upfront cost. It shows its age and wear, but it remains a sensible choice for commuting, errands, or as an inexpensive backup vehicle. Priced to move, this is a great opportunity to get behind the wheel at an accessible price point.",
