      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "If you\u2019re after a budget-friendly car with plenty of potential, this one could be a great fit. It\u2019s being sold in poor condition, so it\u2019s best suited for someone handy, a project buyer, or anyone looking for a solid parts car. That said, it still has a lot to offer at an approachable price, and with the right attention it could be a rewarding little opportunity. I\u2019m aiming to be straightforward here\u2014what you see is what you get, and for the money, it\u2019s a chance to pick up a car without spending a fortune.",
      "price": 6800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with strong enthusiast upside. The drivetrain pulls through the rev range, steering feels direct, and the chassis has the kind of analog character that makes these worth saving. Advertised in poor condition, so expect cosmetic wear, age-related faults, and deferred maintenance, but it presents as a very workable platform for a budget build, parts donor, or weekend resurrection. Great candidate for someone who knows their way around mechanicals and wants an affordable entry point with real potential.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap and honest. Runs, drives, gets the job done. Rough around the edges, priced to move fast. Great beater, work car, or project. First with cash takes it.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A car with honest character and plenty of story left to tell, this ride is perfect for someone who sees potential where others just see age. It has that unmistakable lived-in charm, the kind of vehicle that feels ready for a second chapter\u2014whether as a dependable around-town runabout, a hands-on project, or simply an inexpensive way to get behind the wheel. If you appreciate grit, personality, and value, this one has the makings of a rewarding find.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers a practical way to get on the road without overspending. It shows its age, but it still delivers solid everyday usefulness with a comfortable cabin, straightforward operation, and the kind of value that makes sense for a commuter, first-time buyer, or project-minded shopper. If you want an inexpensive vehicle with honest appeal and plenty of potential, this is a smart buy at an accessible price.",
      "price": 5995.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    }
